race.comment: The stayers kick us off. SIR LAMORAK (1) hasn't been too far away in harder Eagle Farm contests of late and is sure to find this assignment much more to his liking. Gets plenty of weight relief with the 3kg claim and should be able to sit up on speed from the low draw. Rates the testing material. WAGGA WAGGA (4) placed over this track and trip last time out and looks to be working up to another victory. Capable of another strong showing. LEGEND OF KINGS (2) will be ready to peak now fourth-up from the break and must be respected out of the champion Waller yard. Top-three credentials. FLASH PRINCE (6) rounds out the selections.
